4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed to equip individuals with the essential skills to enter the cybersecurity field, even without prior experience. Over 16 weeks, students attend three live online classes each week, with a maximum of 16 participants per class. The curriculum covers foundational knowledge in Windows, Linux, networking, and server administration, alongside specialized topics such as cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence. Graduates receive an official completion certificate recognized by various institutions. Classes are available in English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop